def sensation_analyse(text,emotion_dict,emotion_degree_dict=''):
    ''''''
    words = list(jieba.cut(text))
    emotion_score = 0
    if len(emotion_degree_dict) != 0:
        # 
        for i, word in enumerate(words):
            score = 0
            if word in emotion_dict['word'].values:
                score = emotion_dict[emotion_dict['word'].values==word].iloc[0,1]
                if words[i-1] in emotion_degree_dict['word'].values:
                    degree = emotion_degree_dict[emotion_degree_dict['word'].values == words[i-1]].iloc[0,1]
                    score = score * degree
            emotion_score += score
    else:
        # 
        for word in words:
            score = 0
            if word in emotion_dict['word'].values:
                score = emotion_dict[emotion_dict['word'].values==word].iloc[0,1]
            emotion_score += score
    return emotion_score

# 
def get_comment_score(comment_data,emotion_dict,emotion_degree_dict=''):
    analyse_score = []
    for comment in comment_data['comment']:
        emotion_score = sensation_analyse(comment,emotion_dict,emotion_degree_dict)
        if emotion_score < 0:
            emotion_score = -1
        elif emotion_score > 0:
            emotion_score = 1
        else:
            emotion_score = 0
        analyse_score.append(emotion_score)
    return analyse_score

def performance_test(comment_type,name,y_test,y_pred,concision=True):
    # 
    accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred)
    # 
    precision = precision_score(y_test, y_pred, average='weighted') 
    # 
    recall = recall_score(y_test, y_pred, average='weighted')
    # F1
    f1 = f1_score(y_test, y_pred, average='weighted')
    # 
    class_report = classification_report(y_test, y_pred)
    # 
    conf_matrix = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred)
    result = {'comment_type':[comment_type],'model':[name],'accuracy':[accuracy],'precision':[precision],'recall':[recall],'f1':[f1]}
    result = pd.DataFrame(result)  # dataframe
    if concision:
        return result
    else:
        print("Accuracy:", accuracy)
        print("Precision:", precision)
        print("Recall:", recall)
        print("F1 Score:", f1)
        print("Confusion Matrix:")
        print(conf_matrix)
        print("Classification Report:")
        print(class_report)

model = gensim.models.Word2Vec.load('data/words.model')

words_positive = []
for i in words_seed_positive['word']:
    for j in model.wv.most_similar(positive=i,topn=1000):
        if list(j)[1] > 0.5:
            # 0-7
            words_positive.append([j[0], (j[1]*2-1)*6+1])
words_positive = pd.DataFrame(words_positive)

words_negative = []
for i in words_seed_negative['word']:
    for j in model.wv.most_similar(positive=i,topn=500):
        if list(j)[1] > 0.5:
            # 0-7
            words_negative.append([j[0], -((j[1]*2-1)*6+1)])
words_negative = pd.DataFrame(words_negative)

words_positive.columns = ['word','score']
words_negative.columns = ['word','score']
